### AI Chatbot Endpoints Testing

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7777
@token = your-jwt-token-here

### 1. Get Suggested Questions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chatbot/suggested-questions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Send a Message to Chatbot
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatbot/message
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What receipts do I have?"
}

### 3. Ask about spending
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatbot/message
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "How much have I spent this month?"
}

### 4. Ask about warranties
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatbot/message
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Which warranties are expiring soon?"
}

### 5. Get Conversation History
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chatbot/history?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Clear Conversation History
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/chatbot/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

